WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.820 --> 00:00:07.774
Dear believers, today in the Gospel
we will start reflecting from the

00:00:07.774 --> 00:00:15.308
last sentence: "Whoever is not with
me is against me, and whoever does

00:00:15.308 --> 00:00:21.104
not gather with me scatters." This
sentence immediately highlights an

00:00:21.104 --> 00:00:24.581
important point: we cannot be neutral.

00:00:24.581 --> 00:00:27.479
Jesus demands a definitive commitment.

00:00:27.479 --> 00:00:32.695
Either you are with God or you are not.

00:00:33.295 --> 00:00:35.623
So, you can't be wishy-washy.

00:00:35.623 --> 00:00:41.213
That's why it says, whoever
is not with me is against me.

00:00:41.213 --> 00:00:45.405
If you are with Jesus,
you are his follower.

00:00:45.405 --> 00:00:50.994
Because if you can do good
deeds and you don't, you are

00:00:50.994 --> 00:00:52.391
automatically against Jesus.

00:00:52.391 --> 00:00:57.049
And that's important today because
believers today like to calculate.

00:00:57.049 --> 00:01:03.104
They like to be a believer in the
morning and then cooperate with

00:01:03.104 --> 00:01:06.365
Satan in the evening, and so on.

00:01:06.465 --> 00:01:13.713
So we see among you, the youth, research
shows, especially in America, that

00:01:13.713 --> 00:01:17.058
there is increasing interest in whom?

00:01:17.058 --> 00:01:18.173
In Satan.

00:01:18.173 --> 00:01:22.076
So today, Jesus performs a double miracle.

00:01:22.076 --> 00:01:25.979
He casts out Satan,
performing an exorcism.

00:01:25.979 --> 00:01:33.228
In this exorcism, not only did
he free this man who was mute,

00:01:33.228 --> 00:01:36.573
but he also made him speak.

00:01:36.573 --> 00:01:43.822
Now I ask you, how many people today
truly believe in this spiritual

00:01:43.822 --> 00:01:46.610
world of possession and evil?

00:01:47.789 --> 00:01:48.728
Very few.

00:01:48.728 --> 00:01:54.824
But on the other hand, how does
possession occur, how do such things

00:01:54.824 --> 00:01:57.169
happen that someone becomes possessed?

00:01:57.169 --> 00:01:59.515
It's precisely what I mentioned.

00:01:59.515 --> 00:02:06.550
There is a great, let's say, a great
interest in Satan, in his power, in

00:02:06.550 --> 00:02:12.647
his miracles, and in everything he
offers among a certain group of people.

00:02:12.647 --> 00:02:19.682
For others, they end up in the bondage
of evil because they deny that it

00:02:19.682 --> 00:02:22.965
exists at all, that it doesn't exist.

00:02:23.370 --> 00:02:29.640
And then you will often find in some
biblical commentaries and explanations

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:34.343
that Jesus never actually performed
exorcisms, but only healings.

00:02:34.343 --> 00:02:40.091
However, if you carefully read
the Gospels, you will see that

00:02:40.091 --> 00:02:43.226
there are more than 40 healings.

00:02:43.226 --> 00:02:48.452
There are more than 40 healings
but also two exorcisms.

00:02:48.452 --> 00:02:52.110
So how can we distinguish between them?

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:59.644
So when Jesus, make room to bring it
out because if it's maybe a call or

00:02:59.644 --> 00:03:01.908
something, don't close the entrances.

00:03:01.908 --> 00:03:08.700
So if it's a matter of exorcism,
what we can see in the Gospel as

00:03:08.700 --> 00:03:15.039
well as today, Jesus doesn't take
oil to anoint the sick to heal them.

00:03:15.039 --> 00:03:21.378
Jesus doesn't touch those He intended
to heal and cure, then He works in

00:03:21.378 --> 00:03:24.095
that way by physically touching them.

00:03:25.415 --> 00:03:29.402
He makes a gesture or
uses oil or something.

00:03:29.402 --> 00:03:33.390
However, in exorcism, we see
Jesus expelling demons solely

00:03:33.390 --> 00:03:35.605
with His authority and word.

00:03:35.605 --> 00:03:41.808
So, that's the real thing when He
says the Kingdom of God has come.

00:03:41.808 --> 00:03:48.454
And now if we today... If we have such
faith, we haven't even decided for

00:03:48.454 --> 00:03:51.113
sure what we're really interested in.

00:03:51.113 --> 00:03:56.430
We're a bit intrigued by Jesus, His
power, exorcisms, and those topics.

00:03:56.430 --> 00:04:01.759
On the other hand, so many believers
today, including some preachers,

00:04:01.759 --> 00:04:06.604
only talk about Satan, his
power, and other related topics.

00:04:06.604 --> 00:04:09.511
We sometimes become a bit confused.

00:04:09.511 --> 00:04:16.294
That's why Jesus says today, "Whoever
is not with me is against me." You

00:04:16.294 --> 00:04:23.077
can't say you are with Jesus and deny
that people have problems with demons,

00:04:23.077 --> 00:04:25.985
that people have problems with Satan.

00:04:26.344 --> 00:04:32.109
There is never a time when Satan,
the Devil, Lucifer, is not at work.

00:04:32.109 --> 00:04:33.345
It's so absurd.

00:04:33.345 --> 00:04:38.286
Because if you deny that, you
deny the very reason Jesus came.

00:04:38.286 --> 00:04:43.227
And here in today's Gospel, we hear
about... The Pharisees are astonished,

00:04:43.227 --> 00:04:48.168
meaning the Pharisees knew everything,
they were present at some of the

00:04:48.168 --> 00:04:53.110
exorcisms Jesus performed, and
it was hard for them to admit it.

00:04:53.110 --> 00:04:55.664
And what did they say?

00:04:55.664 --> 00:05:02.818
Maybe you are doing this with the help
of Beelzebub, the prince of demons.

00:05:02.818 --> 00:05:08.439
See what human pride is, see
what jealousy and vanity are.

00:05:08.439 --> 00:05:13.548
Even today, people who practice
exorcism—thank God there are exorcists

00:05:13.548 --> 00:05:19.169
and people who help others—will
often be mocked and told, "Well,

00:05:19.169 --> 00:05:24.789
those are all just mentally ill
people, there's nothing to it."

00:05:25.390 --> 00:05:31.867
And then we won't do that, so are you for
Jesus, have you decided, have you read

00:05:31.867 --> 00:05:34.534
the Gospel, what does the Gospel say?

00:05:34.534 --> 00:05:41.011
You see, it would be great if the truth
is what the Pharisees want to tell Jesus

00:05:41.011 --> 00:05:45.964
today in the Gospel, that the kingdom
of Satan is divided within itself.

00:05:45.964 --> 00:05:51.680
So imagine if Jesus really did that with
the help of Beelzebub, then that's top.

00:05:52.690 --> 00:05:58.861
Because it says only a stronger
one can defeat the strong one.

00:05:58.861 --> 00:06:04.003
That would mean that Jesus defeated
Satan, entered his kingdom,

00:06:04.003 --> 00:06:06.575
caused division, and took control.

00:06:06.575 --> 00:06:09.146
However, that's not the case.

00:06:09.146 --> 00:06:14.803
And the Pharisees, simply out of
jealousy, couldn't accept the way

00:06:14.803 --> 00:06:20.974
Jesus cast out demons with his word,
in other words, performed exorcisms.

00:06:20.974 --> 00:06:25.599
And the witnesses likely saw
manifestations in those individuals.

00:06:25.599 --> 00:06:30.737
They surely saw these people displaying
some strange signs—physical ones,

00:06:30.737 --> 00:06:37.931
changes in voice, smell—and yet they
still said, "No, no, no, no, no. You

00:06:37.931 --> 00:06:45.639
are doing this with the help of this."
I tell you, today, very few Christians

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:52.832
and those who talk about Jesus believe
that Satan, Lucifer, and the one who

00:06:52.832 --> 00:06:55.916
continues to deceive people still exist.

00:06:55.916 --> 00:07:01.568
Nowadays, it's especially easy
for him because with the kind of

00:07:01.568 --> 00:07:08.248
faith we have and the way we speak,
wanting to relativize everything, he

00:07:08.248 --> 00:07:11.844
doesn't have to struggle much at all.

00:07:12.245 --> 00:07:18.017
And another interesting question
that Jesus poses to them, the

00:07:18.017 --> 00:07:24.367
Pharisees who do not believe in
the exorcism they just witnessed.

00:07:24.367 --> 00:07:31.871
Jesus says, well, if I do this by
Beelzebub, how did your ancestors,

00:07:31.871 --> 00:07:41.107
how in the Old Testament, how did you
Jews, how did you help people, how did

00:07:41.107 --> 00:07:44.570
you perform exorcisms in your time?

00:07:44.570 --> 00:07:52.075
If I do it this way, by whom
do they perform such signs?

00:07:53.659 --> 00:07:55.858
Because Jesus knows everything.

00:07:55.858 --> 00:07:59.707
And what is Jesus alluding to here?

00:07:59.707 --> 00:08:06.853
Do you perhaps know of any example
of exorcism in the Old Testament?

00:08:06.853 --> 00:08:10.701
Here, we are listening
about Jesus' miracles.

00:08:10.701 --> 00:08:12.350
There is one.

00:08:12.350 --> 00:08:18.947
So if you have ever read
the book of Tobit, read the

00:08:18.947 --> 00:08:21.146
third chapter, eighth verse.

00:08:21.146 --> 00:08:23.895
So, what is it about?

00:08:26.415 --> 00:08:33.315
So, if we talk about the spiritual world,
there are different kinds of demons.

00:08:34.275 --> 00:08:42.490
I won't go into detail about
all of them and their missions.

00:08:42.490 --> 00:08:46.597
Each demon has its own mission.

00:08:46.597 --> 00:08:57.551
However, in the Book of Tobit, we can
find the name of a demon called Asmodeus.

00:08:57.551 --> 00:08:58.235
Asmodeus.

00:08:58.235 --> 00:09:06.451
The story is about Tobias needing
to marry Sarah, but Sarah had

00:09:06.451 --> 00:09:09.189
several husbands before him.

00:09:09.189 --> 00:09:16.719
And each husband would die before
the marriage could be consummated.

00:09:18.520 --> 00:09:26.021
So here we are talking about an
influential demon, a demon of

00:09:26.021 --> 00:09:29.771
lust and a demon of jealousy.

00:09:29.771 --> 00:09:39.147
He was so jealous of Sara that every
man who approached her ended up dead.

00:09:39.147 --> 00:09:42.273
I'm not talking about oppression.

00:09:42.273 --> 00:09:48.524
I'm talking about seven
husbands who died in that way.

00:09:48.524 --> 00:09:52.899
And Rafael helps Tobi to marry Sara.

00:09:52.899 --> 00:09:55.400
However, Tobi is afraid.

00:09:56.319 --> 00:10:02.188
If he knows that seven husbands
before him died as soon as they

00:10:02.188 --> 00:10:04.896
married her because of that demon.

00:10:04.896 --> 00:10:09.861
And the angel, Raphael, advises
Tobit... How to perform an exorcism?

00:10:09.861 --> 00:10:13.924
How to protect himself
and how to be saved?

00:10:13.924 --> 00:10:22.500
And he says in the sixth chapter, verse
15, "I am afraid that if I go to her, I

00:10:22.500 --> 00:10:29.722
will die like those before me, because
she is loved by a demon who harms no

00:10:29.722 --> 00:10:36.493
one except those who approach her." If
you research a bit more about that demon

00:10:36.493 --> 00:10:42.812
Asmodeus, you will see that he has much
more influence, especially related to the

00:10:42.812 --> 00:10:50.035
sins of lust and jealousy, but there are
many others who each have their own role.

00:10:50.195 --> 00:10:53.835
However, what happens next?

00:10:56.825 --> 00:11:04.054
If you look at it in this spiritual
context, there is a demon tax for all the

00:11:04.054 --> 00:11:07.031
demons that exist, each having its role.

00:11:07.031 --> 00:11:11.283
So, there is this demon
Asmodeus who attacks the family.

00:11:11.283 --> 00:11:15.536
Therefore, against every demon,
there is an angel who fights.

00:11:15.536 --> 00:11:20.213
And that is why Raphael advises
Tobias here, and in translation,

00:11:20.213 --> 00:11:22.339
his name means God's Medicine.

00:11:22.739 --> 00:11:24.541
So, God's Medicine.

00:11:24.541 --> 00:11:30.545
And you see, he further
tells him what to do.

00:11:30.545 --> 00:11:37.149
And you will find there how
Raphael advises what to do.

00:11:37.149 --> 00:11:43.754
To approach Sarah, to burn some
incense, and before they consummate

00:11:43.754 --> 00:11:46.756
their marriage, to pray together.

00:11:46.756 --> 00:11:53.360
And in this way, the demon
Asmodeus, who had already killed

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:56.362
her seven husbands, will leave.

00:11:56.362 --> 00:11:59.364
What do we see here?

00:11:59.464 --> 00:12:04.416
We are talking about exorcism
in the Old Testament.

00:12:04.416 --> 00:12:09.368
And what advice did the
Angel Raphael give them?

00:12:09.368 --> 00:12:11.019
Fasting and prayer.

00:12:11.019 --> 00:12:17.621
So why are you surprised that spiritual
problems prevail in our families?

00:12:17.621 --> 00:12:19.272
Intolerance and discord.

00:12:19.272 --> 00:12:23.123
Why are some marriages a living hell?

00:12:23.123 --> 00:12:30.826
It doesn't always mean that this demon
is attacking the family, but it's good

00:12:30.826 --> 00:12:39.079
to know that there is a demon whose
role is to literally attack the family.

00:12:39.180 --> 00:12:43.240
And now look, you have families,
especially married couples,

00:12:43.240 --> 00:12:45.045
who don't function well.

00:12:45.045 --> 00:12:47.752
Constant intolerance, constant
fighting, constant jealousy.

00:12:47.752 --> 00:12:54.971
It could be that one day you woke
up on the wrong side of the bed

00:12:54.971 --> 00:12:57.227
and you're irritable and tired.

00:12:57.227 --> 00:13:01.739
But how do constant fights break
out over unnecessary things?

00:13:01.739 --> 00:13:08.957
How many of you complain to us priests in
confession about such a crisis and such

00:13:08.957 --> 00:13:11.665
a spiritual atmosphere in your family?

00:13:12.905 --> 00:13:18.983
Conflict with children, disrespect,
cursing, and... This demon is typically

00:13:18.983 --> 00:13:25.061
more associated with women, but it
also suggestively influences men.

00:13:25.061 --> 00:13:28.707
It suggestively influences men as well.

00:13:28.707 --> 00:13:35.393
It even has the power to create
obstacles to prevent something

00:13:35.393 --> 00:13:37.824
dear from being achieved.

00:13:40.495 --> 00:13:46.275
Please, I just want to let you know that
something spiritual like this exists.

00:13:46.545 --> 00:13:51.721
You don't have to immediately demonize
everything and scrutinize your marriage,

00:13:51.721 --> 00:13:54.074
attributing everything to a demon.

00:13:54.074 --> 00:14:00.662
Of course, many times we are responsible
ourselves, but if you were to look,

00:14:00.662 --> 00:14:03.956
besides this demon, there are four more.

00:14:03.956 --> 00:14:11.015
I won't explain who they are or
what they do now, but they are all

00:14:11.015 --> 00:14:13.368
very active and very successful.

00:14:13.368 --> 00:14:19.015
If you look at this demon that
attacked the marriage described by

00:14:19.015 --> 00:14:22.310
Tobit, how did they drive it out?

00:14:22.310 --> 00:14:25.322
How did they get rid of it?

00:14:25.322 --> 00:14:25.752
Prayer.

00:14:25.752 --> 00:14:26.183
Prayer.

00:14:26.183 --> 00:14:30.917
So, what problem does a demon
have today in destroying a

00:14:30.917 --> 00:14:33.499
marriage where there is no prayer?

00:14:33.499 --> 00:14:39.524
As I said at the beginning of
the sermon, he doesn't need to do

00:14:39.524 --> 00:14:44.688
much work when he finds an open
field because you are unprotected.

00:14:44.688 --> 00:14:50.713
But, for those of you who feel it,
don't send me messages tomorrow saying

00:14:50.713 --> 00:14:56.738
you heard in the sermon about this
demon and saw it in your marriage.

00:14:56.738 --> 00:14:58.890
We can have a conversation.

00:14:58.890 --> 00:15:00.144
No, you can't.

00:15:00.144 --> 00:15:01.399
Turn to prayer.

00:15:01.399 --> 00:15:02.654
Turn to prayer.

00:15:02.654 --> 00:15:04.745
Why am I saying this?

00:15:04.745 --> 00:15:06.418
Let me ask you.

00:15:06.418 --> 00:15:11.019
If this church were to catch
fire right now, burning, would

00:15:11.019 --> 00:15:13.110
you all start asking questions?

00:15:13.110 --> 00:15:16.038
Is it the outlet or the cable?

00:15:16.038 --> 00:15:18.129
Why did it catch fire?

00:15:18.129 --> 00:15:21.475
Would someone start
coming to the gas stove?

00:15:21.475 --> 00:15:23.984
No, you don't ask such questions.

00:15:23.984 --> 00:15:29.003
When you see a fire, you go
and immediately put it out.

00:15:29.003 --> 00:15:35.277
You don't ask how the fire started,
what the value of this church is if

00:15:35.277 --> 00:15:41.132
it burns down, what will happen to the
instruments, what will happen to the

00:15:41.132 --> 00:15:46.570
altar, where will the sermons be given
from, you don't ask such questions.

00:15:49.860 --> 00:15:55.804
And why did I say that so no one
thinks I'm arrogant, that you

00:15:55.804 --> 00:15:58.352
don't reach out for a conversation?

00:15:58.352 --> 00:16:03.023
Because, my dear ones, the
devil has deceived you a little.

00:16:03.023 --> 00:16:09.393
When you see a problem in your marriage,
in your family, in your personal life,

00:16:09.393 --> 00:16:12.365
don't ask where the evil comes from.

00:16:12.365 --> 00:16:14.064
How powerful is Satan?

00:16:14.064 --> 00:16:16.612
He is really destroying my marriage.

00:16:16.612 --> 00:16:19.160
This is how priests function today.

00:16:20.040 --> 00:16:20.363
Undecided.

00:16:20.363 --> 00:16:22.626
So, this is a time of struggle.

00:16:22.626 --> 00:16:25.537
You see that something is
burning in your marriage.

00:16:25.537 --> 00:16:28.123
Your house is burning,
your marriage is burning.

00:16:28.123 --> 00:16:31.680
You go and put out the fire,
you don't ask questions.

00:16:31.680 --> 00:16:35.561
But many like to come and just
ask questions, talk about Satan.

00:16:35.561 --> 00:16:41.058
And I just said a moment ago, there's no
time to talk about Satan, nor should we.

00:16:41.058 --> 00:16:42.674
Instead, put out the fire.

00:16:42.674 --> 00:16:44.614
This is a time of struggle.

00:16:44.854 --> 00:16:50.586
And God has given us grace, given us
the means to extinguish such situations.

00:16:50.586 --> 00:16:56.728
So that the devil flees, if I interpreted
this correctly, read the Book of Tobit

00:16:56.728 --> 00:17:02.050
again to see how they saved and protected
their marriage—they lit incense and

00:17:02.050 --> 00:17:04.507
started praying, and the demon left.

00:17:04.507 --> 00:17:10.239
Don't talk too much about what that
demon is doing in your family, how

00:17:10.239 --> 00:17:14.743
your husband or wife is unbearable,
intolerant, nervous, and so on.

00:17:14.743 --> 00:17:15.561
Start praying.

00:17:15.561 --> 00:17:20.475
No priest or conversation will help
you if you don't start praying.

00:17:20.475 --> 00:17:27.025
And how many marriages, if you look at the
statistics, even in Croatia, even on our

00:17:27.025 --> 00:17:32.348
continent, how many people this demon has
managed to incite to destroy marriages,

00:17:32.348 --> 00:17:34.804
and how many people are divorced.

00:17:35.344 --> 00:17:40.848
I repeat, it's not always because of
demons, but I'm sure that families

00:17:40.848 --> 00:17:46.352
where there is no prayer are much more
susceptible to such demonic influences,

00:17:46.352 --> 00:17:51.855
because I say... It's not normal for
your partner to be constantly jealous,

00:17:51.855 --> 00:17:56.512
constantly nervous, always provoking
you, always causing unrest in the house.

00:17:56.512 --> 00:17:57.782
That's not normal.

00:17:57.782 --> 00:18:03.710
And on the other hand, they'll tell
you in the evening, I love you.

00:18:04.189 --> 00:18:05.613
Something's not right.

00:18:05.613 --> 00:18:07.036
Something's not right.

00:18:07.036 --> 00:18:13.203
And that's why I say, we shouldn't
talk about demons, we should act.

00:18:13.203 --> 00:18:15.100
Take action and pray.

00:18:15.100 --> 00:18:19.370
We have the means and
we shouldn't be afraid.

00:18:19.370 --> 00:18:22.690
If you start praying, it will disappear.

00:18:22.690 --> 00:18:24.113
Evil will disappear.

00:18:24.113 --> 00:18:29.331
So, first and foremost, we
have the sacraments as a means.

00:18:29.331 --> 00:18:31.703
Confession is the best exorcism.

00:18:31.703 --> 00:18:34.550
Because there, you speak the truth.

00:18:34.550 --> 00:18:38.345
And that's where the
real battles are fought.

00:18:39.379 --> 00:18:44.683
Look at those who are going
through marital crises, ask them—

00:18:44.683 --> 00:18:51.433
I know many of you will message me
tomorrow, so I'm posing this question

00:18:51.433 --> 00:18:54.808
in advance to save you a trip.

00:18:54.808 --> 00:19:02.040
Seek help and ask your partner when was
the last time they went to confession.

00:19:02.040 --> 00:19:06.862
It's a powerful exorcism because
there, we are all honest,

00:19:06.862 --> 00:19:09.754
and the truth sets us free.

00:19:09.754 --> 00:19:14.829
And let's not forget that every
demon, every Satan, and the devil

00:19:14.829 --> 00:19:17.366
himself is the father of lies.

00:19:17.366 --> 00:19:21.595
And everything that is a lie,
everything that is twisted,

00:19:21.595 --> 00:19:23.709
means you are under influence.

00:19:23.709 --> 00:19:29.630
When you go sincerely and confess, then
Satan has no influence on your marriage.

00:19:29.630 --> 00:19:35.127
As long as you persistently reject
the sacraments in your marriage or any

00:19:35.127 --> 00:19:40.625
family relationship, you will not defeat
Satan, nor will you easily find peace.

00:19:40.905 --> 00:19:41.755
You won't.

00:19:41.755 --> 00:19:44.307
The first thing is the sacraments.

00:19:44.307 --> 00:19:49.410
At baptism, do the godparents and
others ask, "Do you renounce Satan?"

00:19:49.410 --> 00:19:52.387
Don't we say the same at confirmation?

00:19:52.387 --> 00:19:58.340
And when we renew our faith, don't we
again confess that we renounce Satan?

00:19:58.340 --> 00:19:59.616
This is important.

00:19:59.616 --> 00:20:02.168
Renounce sin, its
seductions, renounce Satan.

00:20:02.168 --> 00:20:07.271
That's why I say, if you want to mend
interpersonal relationships, marriages,

00:20:07.271 --> 00:20:13.225
and so on, start by cleansing the heart
of sin, and blessings will follow.

00:20:13.225 --> 00:20:15.091
Demons will all leave.

00:20:15.091 --> 00:20:18.825
You don't need to talk about their power.

00:20:18.825 --> 00:20:23.025
Another thing, blessed items
are a form of protection.

00:20:26.215 --> 00:20:30.040
How will the demon leave your house
when you barely bought a small cross

00:20:30.040 --> 00:20:34.413
and put it somewhere behind a book so
no one can see it, are you ashamed?

00:20:34.413 --> 00:20:39.058
No, take the cross, put it in the house
so that anyone who enters can see it,

00:20:39.058 --> 00:20:41.244
and both Satan and the enemy will flee.

00:20:41.244 --> 00:20:45.617
And when I have a house blessing, I
can't even find where the cross is with

00:20:45.617 --> 00:20:47.530
all my glasses, man, for God's sake.

00:20:47.530 --> 00:20:52.596
And today, if possible, it should be some
modern one without Jesus on it, just a

00:20:52.596 --> 00:20:55.129
bit of shiny glass to make it trendy.

00:20:58.399 --> 00:21:04.420
Put up a normal cross with Jesus
on it, and let everyone see it.

00:21:04.420 --> 00:21:10.441
If someone can't stand your cross,
they don't need to be in your house;

00:21:10.441 --> 00:21:13.022
drive them away with that cross.

00:21:13.022 --> 00:21:18.612
In serious exorcisms, when you place
a cross on someone's forehead or body,

00:21:18.612 --> 00:21:21.623
they scream and say it burns them.

00:21:21.623 --> 00:21:28.074
So if someone is bothered by the sight
of your cross, we have a situation

00:21:28.074 --> 00:21:32.375
where we are removing crosses from
our institutions and everything.

00:21:33.915 --> 00:21:36.387
Who is bothered by the cross?

00:21:36.387 --> 00:21:38.860
Who is burned by the cross?

00:21:38.860 --> 00:21:39.272
Who?

00:21:39.272 --> 00:21:39.684
Who?

00:21:39.684 --> 00:21:41.745
So, let's be believers, people.

00:21:41.745 --> 00:21:46.278
I say, in the sacraments, we
have means, other blessed things.

00:21:46.278 --> 00:21:49.987
The first is the cross,
blessed water, exorcised salt.

00:21:49.987 --> 00:21:54.932
But I must warn you, many of
you are using them magically.

00:21:54.932 --> 00:22:00.289
You take blessed water and salt,
then you put it in your husband's

00:22:00.289 --> 00:22:04.823
dinner, breakfast, in everything, as
if magically, thinking the evil will

00:22:04.823 --> 00:22:08.120
disappear, but you have no faith at all.

00:22:08.205 --> 00:22:13.657
Cooking beans in blessed water won't
free you just because you drink

00:22:13.657 --> 00:22:16.383
blessed water and lick blessed salt.

00:22:16.383 --> 00:22:20.927
It will help you, but
only if you have faith.

00:22:20.927 --> 00:22:27.289
I must warn you, especially you older
believers, please don't do it like magic.

00:22:27.289 --> 00:22:32.287
Blessed salt, blessed water, the
cross—these can help, but if you

00:22:32.287 --> 00:22:35.467
don't have faith, it won't do much.

00:22:35.467 --> 00:22:42.283
You can wear ten medals around your neck,
but without faith, it won't help you.

00:22:42.283 --> 00:22:47.736
You can put a rosary in your
car for protection, but without

00:22:47.736 --> 00:22:52.280
faith and a personal relationship
with God, it won't help.

00:22:52.460 --> 00:22:59.367
That's why I say, use these things, they
are a means in the sacraments, but not to

00:22:59.367 --> 00:23:06.274
be magic where I sprinkle a little salt
and water but don't go to Mass on Sunday.

00:23:06.274 --> 00:23:07.899
It won't help you.

00:23:07.899 --> 00:23:12.775
First, you go to Mass, and
then you bless your space, car,

00:23:12.775 --> 00:23:14.806
cat, and everything you have.

00:23:14.806 --> 00:23:16.431
Please, first the sacraments.

00:23:16.431 --> 00:23:22.120
I encourage you, and I feel that
sometimes we overdo it with these things.

00:23:22.940 --> 00:23:27.925
Highlighting evil, highlighting the
disorder in our lives, all the chaos,

00:23:27.925 --> 00:23:33.818
putting too much emphasis on that,
where is Jesus in the whole story?

00:23:33.818 --> 00:23:38.350
Look, today in the Gospel,
with one word, Satan flees.

00:23:38.350 --> 00:23:43.336
Let's return to Jesus so
that Jesus is in our hearts.

00:23:43.336 --> 00:23:45.602
Satan will flee from us.

00:23:45.602 --> 00:23:50.135
And don't be afraid of losing
so-called friends and acquaintances.

00:23:50.475 --> 00:23:55.686
If you have Jesus in your heart, you
will lose half the people you know.

00:23:55.686 --> 00:23:56.380
Thank God.

00:23:56.380 --> 00:23:57.423
A natural exorcism.

00:23:57.423 --> 00:23:59.855
They flee from you like the devil.

00:24:03.040 --> 00:24:11.053
But I ask individuals, even some of
you whom I know, how is it that you

00:24:11.053 --> 00:24:17.563
are a magnet for negative people
instead of them running away from you?

00:24:17.563 --> 00:24:19.066
Good question, right?

00:24:19.066 --> 00:24:26.077
As believers, how is it that you, as
a believer who carries Jesus, instead

00:24:26.077 --> 00:24:30.585
of those negative people—what we
would call naughty children—running

00:24:30.585 --> 00:24:33.590
away from you, you attract them?

00:24:33.850 --> 00:24:36.318
You gather them and want change.

00:24:36.318 --> 00:24:40.021
You want to have contact with all of them.

00:24:40.021 --> 00:24:43.724
You want to have those
people in every sphere.

00:24:43.724 --> 00:24:44.958
It doesn't work.

00:24:44.958 --> 00:24:51.129
If any of you here are like that, the
environment, the people around you, the

00:24:51.129 --> 00:24:54.010
ambiance, all of that is very important.

00:24:54.010 --> 00:24:55.655
It's all spiritual space.

00:24:55.655 --> 00:24:57.712
I call it spiritual ecology.

00:24:57.712 --> 00:25:00.592
It's not the same where you are.

00:25:00.592 --> 00:25:05.530
In places with a high concentration
of sin, the atmosphere is different.

00:25:05.770 --> 00:25:10.971
How then can someone who is a believer
enjoy and be in that environment?

00:25:10.971 --> 00:25:15.801
How can you be with people who
you know are great sinners, who

00:25:15.801 --> 00:25:19.888
curse constantly, who bring curses
upon you and that spiritual space

00:25:19.888 --> 00:25:22.117
every time they open their mouths?

00:25:22.117 --> 00:25:27.690
If you want to keep in contact with
such people, it only means that your

00:25:27.690 --> 00:25:29.919
heart might be poisoned as well.

00:25:29.919 --> 00:25:34.030
If you have people around you who
constantly speak ill of others

00:25:34.030 --> 00:25:37.797
and you keep associating with
them, it will poison you too.

00:25:37.797 --> 00:25:40.195
Do you understand the
term spiritual ecology?

00:25:40.195 --> 00:25:45.332
How many times has it been said about
those who curse, that if you constantly

00:25:45.332 --> 00:25:48.072
listen to it, you will start cursing too.

00:25:48.072 --> 00:25:49.100
Because it's contagious.

00:25:49.100 --> 00:25:51.497
And you need to act on that.

00:25:51.497 --> 00:25:55.607
So, if you belong to Christ, as
I started this sermon, whoever

00:25:55.607 --> 00:25:58.005
is not with me is against me.

00:25:58.185 --> 00:26:00.503
Today is a time for commitment.

00:26:00.503 --> 00:26:03.595
Are you with Jesus, in Jesus, or not?

00:26:03.595 --> 00:26:05.141
You can't make compromises.

00:26:05.141 --> 00:26:10.552
Those who come to church occasionally
but keep in touch with the whole world,

00:26:10.552 --> 00:26:15.189
living like everyone else, I'm not
judging or calling anyone out here.

00:26:15.189 --> 00:26:20.214
I'm just stating the facts and what
is true in the spiritual world.

00:26:20.214 --> 00:26:21.760
That's how it is.

00:26:22.139 --> 00:26:27.195
You can't have peace and not be influenced
by the devil and demons if you're

00:26:27.195 --> 00:26:29.554
surrounded by people who drag them along.

00:26:29.554 --> 00:26:30.902
It's not the same.

00:26:30.902 --> 00:26:35.621
You young people think we're old-fashioned
and stupid when we talk to you about

00:26:35.621 --> 00:26:40.002
clubs, but no, you need to know
where you should and shouldn't go.

00:26:40.002 --> 00:26:41.687
Choose wisely where you go.

00:26:41.687 --> 00:26:45.394
It's not the same as entering
some dark hole, where there's

00:26:45.394 --> 00:26:47.080
all sorts of dark spirits.

00:26:48.885 --> 00:26:51.625
It's not about the
people, but the spirits.

00:26:51.625 --> 00:26:56.764
I only mentioned one spirit here that the
Bible talks about and how it influences.

00:26:56.764 --> 00:27:00.874
If I were to explain all the
others, I think you wouldn't

00:27:00.874 --> 00:27:02.930
even go to the post office.

00:27:02.930 --> 00:27:06.355
We don't see them physically,
but we feel them spiritually.

00:27:06.355 --> 00:27:10.466
And now someone listening to this
might say, "There they go again,

00:27:10.466 --> 00:27:14.235
scaring us with devils and other
things." I'm just telling you.

00:27:16.010 --> 00:27:17.942
Do you feel clean?

00:27:17.942 --> 00:27:19.874
Do you feel clean?

00:27:19.874 --> 00:27:26.153
There are places where, when I go
out, I don't feel spiritually clean.

00:27:26.153 --> 00:27:30.017
And I believe you can feel that too.

00:27:30.017 --> 00:27:32.915
And that's it, that spiritual world.

00:27:32.915 --> 00:27:36.779
I repeat, there's nothing to be afraid of.

00:27:36.779 --> 00:27:44.024
As Jesus says and as we saw in the
exorcism in Tobit's book, everything can

00:27:44.024 --> 00:27:47.405
be done through prayer and the sacraments.

00:27:47.635 --> 00:27:51.285
Because Jesus gave us the
sacraments for that reason.

00:27:51.285 --> 00:27:56.965
So we can resist the influence of
Satan and talk about the beauty and

00:27:56.965 --> 00:28:01.832
power of Jesus Christ who changed
our lives, who opened our eyes.

00:28:01.832 --> 00:28:06.295
Tell others how you found
peace, not how you lost it.

00:28:06.295 --> 00:28:11.162
Tell others what Jesus brought
to you, how He drove out demons

00:28:11.162 --> 00:28:15.625
from you, especially those that
may have oppressed you for years.

00:28:16.025 --> 00:28:18.013
Testify a little for Jesus.

00:28:18.013 --> 00:28:21.193
Speak the truth because
you will encourage someone.

00:28:21.193 --> 00:28:25.567
We never talk about it, but
maybe many would seek help.

00:28:25.567 --> 00:28:29.146
Maybe some would even
come to the Divine Mercy.

00:28:29.146 --> 00:28:35.110
But as much as we share, that's why
I say, we always talk about Satan,

00:28:35.110 --> 00:28:40.676
but let's talk a little about Jesus
and His power, and you'll see how

00:28:40.676 --> 00:28:42.665
the atmosphere and mood change.

00:28:43.305 --> 00:28:43.765
Amen.

